    "description": "<i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >守住神殿</h2>您成为了被女神召唤保护水之神殿的战士。<br><br>随着傍晚的临近，瞄准水之神殿的怪物出现了。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/69023e863f21a846a8897b9184e1a8b4.poster.avif?t=1673251800\" width=500 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/69023e863f21a846a8897b9184e1a8b4.webm?t=1673251800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/69023e863f21a846a8897b9184e1a8b4.mp4?t=1673251800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通过考验</h2>战士，<br>通过 6 次考验以保护水神殿免受怪物的侵害。<br>并成为守护水之神殿，杀怪守护女神的传奇战士！<br>此外，在 神殿射手 的舞台上与其他战士进行一场惊心动魄的 1v1 战斗，尝试最好的战士。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/1c272a8f7e4d325279b1da2a08b12ca0.poster.avif?t=1673251800\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/1c272a8f7e4d325279b1da2a08b12ca0.webm?t=1673251800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/1c272a8f7e4d325279b1da2a08b12ca0.mp4?t=1673251800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为最棒的战士吧</h2>进入游戏后会有教程，可以更直观地轻松开始玩法。<br>墙上有文字说明，所以不难开始。\t<br>同时还加了语音提示，可以更加流畅地玩游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/327df840790476b11a2b0c14bb869000.poster.avif?t=1673251800\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/327df840790476b11a2b0c14bb869000.webm?t=1673251800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808250/extras/327df840790476b11a2b0c14bb869000.mp4?t=1673251800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >#VR射击  # 打击感  #不晕车</h2>像真的一样的真实VR画着一道抛物线，<br>美丽地射箭吧。<br><br>击中目标的时发出啪！的声音和华丽的效果，<br>不仅能更真实地感受到爽快的打击感<br><br>因为没有移动，<br>所以完全不晕车，就可以更加开心地玩游戏。<br><br><br><br><br>特征 :<br>🎯对决！成为最棒的战士吧！<br>🎯瞄准！用弓箭射中移动的靶子！<br>🎯 发射！比任何人都要快速准确地射箭！<br>🎯 拜托！我力量的极限在哪里！ 把箭尽量放远!<br>🏹 头脑全速运转！ 使用所有的感觉背下来！<br>🏹 完成所有单人游戏，解禁BOSS战！<br>🏹 抓住老板会不会产生好的东西...？<br>🏆收集！提高实力，收集所有奖牌！</i>",
